  <summary date="2020-07-08T17:44:38Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Pandemic Authority Suitable To Utilize Reserve Easements Act or the PASTURE Act

This bill provides authority for the Department of Agriculture during a pandemic to permit activities such as emergency haying and grazing on land that is subject to a contract under the Conservation Reserve Program.</summary>
